preference.name: TC_object_type_delegation
preference.preference_description: Configures the Access Manager delegation for object types to a class. The format is typeName:className , which delegates access for named references of the type identified by typeName to the owning class identified by className . By default, the access for the following five object types are delegated to its owning dataset: ImanFile UGPartAttr UGPartAttributesForm UGPartBoundingBoxForm UGPartMassPropsForm You do not need to add entries for these types.
